org.bicycleGeometryWorkshop.attributes

Class AttributeChangeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bicycleGeometryWorkshop.attributes.AttributeChangeEvent

  • public class AttributeChangeEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Event Object for a change in Attribute. This stores the attribute and the previous and current values of the attribute.
